items.name: InvalidContext
desc: InvalidContext: a device was requested that does not exist.

items.name: ScanCanceled
desc: ScanCanceled: the scan was canceled by the user.

items.name: ScanFailed
desc: ScanFailed: an error occurred during scanning.

items.name: ScanInProgress
desc: ScanInProgress: a scan is already in progress on this device that has to end before a new one can be started.

items.name: ScannerNotAvailable
desc: ScannerNotAvailable: the requested device could not be opened.
